ui_elements.text:
Last year I gave the teachers Starbucks gift cards and I bought one for myself. Imagine my horror when I went to use it in January and it rang up zero dollars, as in never turned on.

I paid for cards for 15 teachers between my kids. Horrified the teachers got empty gift cards and mad I paid $$ for empty cards.

 I fixed it later. Still horribly embarrassing.

Double check those physical cards before you gift them at school and add the receipt!

ui_elements.text:
I got a haircut today & left her a $50 Christmas tip. 
After, I  ate lunch at a busy pizza place where you had to wait for a table.
 
I asked the guy waiting ahead of me, if we could share a table and he said yes. 
Long story short, we talked, ate, and at the end, he paid for my meal. 

Feeling blessed and thankful for kind people today.

The post likely failed because no content was actually selected or recorded - the grid appears empty and no caption was entered, so there's nothing to post. To fix this, the user needs to either record new video content using the camera button or select existing clips to create the reel.
